{
  "texts": [
    "To better observe eye movement characteristics, we also include fixation location accuracy (FLA) and fixation duration accuracy (FDA), which range from 0 (worst possible accuracy) to 1 (best).",
    "5 Does ScanEZ Capture Where Readers Fixate, and When They Do So?",
    "We answer this question by replicating the experiments of Deng et al. (2023) and observing ScanEZ performance on naturalistic (EML) data.",
    "foot_2 Comparison with Eyettention.",
    "ScanEZ achieves better (i.e., lower) NLL and NLD under all experimental settings."
  ]
